{"tid":1663971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除左課金，手足們請課血！","createTime":"2019-10-19T18:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T04:29:24.000Z","uid":304758,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10607162ad6be6c97e985b590fb1d6027d38d7c5","tid":1663971,"uid":304758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:08:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的，由於熱血嘅手足們返工返學好忙，放工放學後更忙，紅十字會少左人幫襯！<br />\n<br />\n血液供應非常緊張，唔希望長期病患者冇血用，更唔希望有手足俾狗咬傷或遇到刀手後失救，請大家課血。<br />\n<br />\n前綫要留力，請後援和理非幫忙出大力。這是錢不能取代的，每一次捐血可以救三個人。<br />\n<br />\n我早兩日捐完，仲收到靚靚毛巾。毛巾會送到11月3日。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5e2k7qL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5e2k7qL.png&h=8ca8dfc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"198d62b58b6c880736aa3ffd810f95c785e3d64d","tid":1663971,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"[1020 行動Post] 香港人真係好痴線！不論組織力、耐力、創意玩到咁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eovgRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eovgRS</a>"},{"pid":"3bba7b383ffc4dc4c4ddea71c307d730660040d6","tid":1663971,"uid":304758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:18:40.000Z","msg":"職員話捐血人數真係好慘淡。"},{"pid":"a7698799f1e9e5e937a88b9eca3240c0c33ad549","tid":1663971,"uid":304758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"唔該幫幫手！"},{"pid":"8b27c9933760b989b71150e5734ba58ce35276d4","tid":1663971,"uid":304758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93997017e7180d9d5690238b02fc7bab1b319a9e","tid":1663971,"uid":304758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g